    "Name": "Garm",
    "Details": "This advanced technology variant was introduced during the Jihad, and is a complete revision of the design. The standard fusion engine, gyro, ferro-fibrous armor, and 10 single heat sinks are upgraded to a light fusion engine, an XL gyro, light ferro-fibrous armor, and double heat sinks. These upgrades not only increase the 'Mech's speed to 97.2 km/h, but also allows for increased armor coverage. Finally, the LB-X AC/5 is replaced with a Capellan manufactured plasma rifle, fed by two tons of ammunition.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Extended Torso Twist</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 0.98</color></b>",
